name: Tic Tac Toe
body: A simple implementation of the [minimax](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minimax) algorithm. There is an initial proof of concept in Python, and then a more finely-tuned version in C++. It can be compiled using emscripten, as shown on the projects Github page.
